Name:           spin
Version:        1.5
Release:        alt2_17jpp8
Summary:        A transparent threading solution for non-freezing Swing applications
License:        LGPLv2
Group:          Development/Java
Url:            http://spin.sourceforge.net/
BuildArch:      noarch

Source0:        http://downloads.sourceforge.net/%{name}/%{name}-%{version}-all.zip
